                        <tr>
                          <td class="gutter">
                            <pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre>
                          </td>
                          <td class="code">
                            <pre><span class="line">hexo config theme icarus</span><br></pre>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>
                  </div>
                </figure>


                <p>最后，使用如下命令来启动Hexo本地测试服务器并开始创作。</p>
                <figure class="highlight plaintext hljs" id="code-162244512503082">
                  <figcaption class="level is-mobile">
